      "text": "NEW: A three-time deported illegal immigrant from Honduras is accused of beating a man unconscious and then dragging him behind a dumpster and raping him while he was incapacitated in Suffolk County, New York, @ICEgov announces.\n\nUS Marshals arrested Jose Ignacio Bonilla-Garcia, 32, on April 4 near Richmond, TX, as he was allegedly attempting to flee to Mexico.\n\nICE has since lodged a detainer with the Fort Bend County Jail.\n\nBonilla-Garcia entered the U.S. illegally at least four times and was removed three times in 2020 under Title 42. He then snuck into the country as a gotaway, marking his fourth border crossing.",
      "text_resolved": "NEW: A three-time deported illegal immigrant from Honduras is accused of beating a man unconscious and then dragging him behind a dumpster and raping him while he was incapacitated in Suffolk County, New York, @ICEgov announces.\n\nUS Marshals arrested Jose Ignacio Bonilla-Garcia, 32, on April 4 near Richmond, TX, as he was allegedly attempting to flee to Mexico.\n\nICE has since lodged a detainer with the Fort Bend County Jail.\n\nBonilla-Garcia entered the U.S. illegally at least four times and was removed three times in 2020 under Title 42. He then snuck into the country as a gotaway, marking his fourth border crossing.",
